<chapter id="requirements" xreflabel="Requirements">


<title>Requirements</title>

<section id="rocks-version" xreflabel="Rocks Version">
<title>Rocks Version</title>

<para>

The Area51 Roll is for use on x86 systems (e.g., Pentium and Athlon) and
x86_64 (Opteron and EM64T)
with Rocks version @VERSION@ (@VERSION_NAME@).

</para>

<para>
The Area51 Roll is only installed on the frontend.
</para>

</section>


<section id="other-rolls" xreflabel="Other Rolls">
<title>Other Rolls</title>

<para>

The Area51 Roll is does not require any other Rolls (other than the HPC
Roll) to be installed on the Frontend.
Compatiblity has been verified with the following Rolls.

</para>

<itemizedlist>

<listitem><para>HPC</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Grid</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Intel</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>SGE</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Java</para></listitem>

</itemizedlist>


</section>


</chapter>

